      <data key="d9">2026-07-17T10:31:33.504352+00:00</data>
      <data key="d10">ode. He developed the Bombe, an electromechanical device used to decipher Enigma-encrypted messages.

After the war, Turing worked at the National Physical Laboratory and later at the University of Manchester. He is widely considered the father of theoretical computer science and artificial intelligence. His 1950 paper "Computing Machinery and Intelligence" introduced the Turing Test.</data>
