    <edge source="alan_turing:chunk0" target="Alan Turing">
      <data key="d15">["MENTIONS"]</data>
      <data key="d16">1</data>
      <data key="d17">["Alan Turing was born in London, England in 1912. He studied at King's College, Cambridge and later earned his PhD from Princeton University.\n\nDuring World War II, Turing worked at Bletchley Park, where he played a crucial role in breaking the German Enigma code. He developed the Bombe, an electromechanical device used to decipher Enigma-encrypted messages."]</data>
    </edge>
